p.span: In the fast-paced, ever-growing world of Healthcare, Humana relies on information and data to create superior service for our customers, partners and employees. To ensure that this information is properly aligned with the strategy and mission of the organization, we need professionals who can collect, analyze and develop requirements for strategies necessary to enhance and optimize the data that drives the complex relationships between business functions, legal, compliance, security and IT delivery teams as well as with our customers, providers and business partners. This information is critical to our continued success and the advancement of our strategic objectives.

div.span: Humana Inc., headquartered in Louisville, Ky., is a leading health care company that offers a wide range of insurance products and health and wellness services that incorporate an integrated approach to lifelong well-being. By leveraging the strengths of its core businesses, Humana believes it can better explore opportunities for existing and emerging adjacencies in health care that can further enhance wellness opportunities for the millions of people across the nation with whom the company has relationships.
